## 📌 Featured Projects

### 🔥 Forest Fire Alerting System (IoT + GSM + GPS)
A smart IoT-based system to detect fire and send emergency alerts via GSM with GPS coordinates.

- 🔍 Detects fire using IR sensors  
- 📡 Sends location-based SMS using GPS and GSM modules  
- 🔋 Designed for low power and real-time response  
  

